Package edu.usfca.cs.echan13

Class Song

java.lang.Object
edu.usfca.cs.echan13.Entity
edu.usfca.cs.echan13.Song
public class Song extends Entity
The Song class represents a song. It stores values for the song's title, artist, album, and if it is liked. It extends the Entity class.
